This repository bundles reference implementations of the following algorithms
under their respective upstream licenses:

- NTRU+    : https://github.com/ntruplus/ntruplus
- SMAUG-T  : https://github.com/hmchoe0528/SMAUG-T_public (MIT)
- AIMer    : https://github.com/samsungsds-research-papers/AIMer (MIT)
- HAETAE   : KS X 123456 reference release (MIT)
- common/randombytes.c : MIT, Copyright (c) 2017 Daan Sprenkels
- common/Keccak_avx2, common/keccak4x : Keccak XKCP, CC0 / public domain

The original license/copyright notices in each source file are preserved.
